title: Are there any differenced between these two chests? (multiplier for worlds)
body:
I tried buying the more expensive one and as far as i can tell, theres no difference! is this a mistake? 
https://imgur.com/a/km26h

replies.body: The 490 one is guaranteed to give a skin in the 520 RP tier or higher. The 790 one is guaranteed to give a skin in the 975 RP tier or higher. They are otherwise completely identical.
^ This guy knows whats up. Just here to confirm ^_^
